--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This directory contains tools that help preparing Peacemaker input. These tools
are primarily written in python3 and awk. This file contains short descriptions
of each tool.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

hess2flist.awk:
    Converts an Orca Hessian file to a frequency list file.

vdw_sum_volume.py:
    Calculates the cluster volume using the old, sum-of-spheres approach.

vibspectrum2flist.awk:
    Converts a Turbomole vibspectrum file to a frequency list file.

xyzr.py:
    Creates an xyzr file that can be used as input for quick_gepol.
    Quick_gepol may be obtained upon request from the Peacemaker authors.
